snippet.title: Soft White Underbelly
snippet.description:
Soft White Underbelly interviews and portraits of the human condition by photographer, Mark Laita.

Contact:soft_white_underbelly@yahoo.com

For individuals requesting to be considered for an interview please send a short version of your story, your location and a 10-20 second video of yourself to: soft_white_underbelly@yahoo.com

For ad-free, uncensored versions of SWU videos, as well as some exclusive videos please subscribe to: softwhiteunderbelly.com

Here’s a link to audio only versions of my videos: https://asmrdb.fanlink.to/softwhiteunderbelly
